        <p class="services-p">Motor dealers are expected to consider customer outcomes, customer understanding and the needs of vulnerable customers throughout the sales process.</p>
        <p class="services-p">The FCA increasingly expects firms to demonstrate how customer interests are considered within business operations and customer interactions.</p>
        <p class="services-p">We help firms understand how Consumer Duty principles apply within the context of motor finance and dealership operations.</p>
        <p class="services-p">Our focus is on practical implementation rather than unnecessary complexity.</p>
      </article>

